Definition: showing extreme cupidity
Example: painfully desirous of another's advantages; he was never covetous before he met her; jealous of his success and covetous of his possessions; envious of their art collection
Synonyms: noun, attribute, covetousness, envious, act, envy, feeling, enviousness, jealous, showing, extreme, cupidity, painfully, desirous, of, another, s, advantages, he, was, never, before, met, her, his, success, and, possessions, their, art, collection
Category: adj.all
